abstract_ssm: This collection includes documents related to the title history of a property in the Bushwick neighborhood of Brooklyn on a block between Bushwick and Evergreen Avenues and Hancock Street and Jefferson Avenue.  Also included are a program of the Bushwick Avenue Baptist Church mentioning the sale of the church, a program for a production of the play Cinderella, and a copy photograph of the Junior Choir of the Bushwick Avenue Methodist Episcopal Church.
